WEBVTT

00:07.268 --> 00:09.095
VANESSA: <i>Previously on</i> Penny Dreadful...

00:09.120 --> 00:10.524
DR. SEWARD: <i>What does he want with her?</i>

00:10.549 --> 00:12.218
The Master does not want!

00:12.243 --> 00:13.963
She is already his.

00:14.069 --> 00:16.289
DR. SEWARD: <i>He said that
Vanessa was with the Master.</i>

00:16.314 --> 00:18.041
This is the creature she called Dracula.

00:18.066 --> 00:20.371
I've got to get him to
tell us where she is.

00:20.396 --> 00:21.999
FRANKENSTEIN: <i>We're going
to try to make you healthy.</i>

00:22.077 --> 00:22.970
(LILY SCREAMS)

00:22.995 --> 00:25.408
Do you not see the cruelty of
what you are doing, Victor?

00:25.433 --> 00:28.706
You created life... so let it live.

00:28.731 --> 00:29.439
(SOBBING)

00:29.464 --> 00:31.541
DORIAN: <i>For all her furious power,</i>

00:31.566 --> 00:33.870
your valiant leader was snuffed out.

00:34.001 --> 00:35.037
(BONES CRACKING)

00:36.086 --> 00:37.255
(COUGHING)

00:37.280 --> 00:39.652
JACK: <i>Will we go to the
Highlands when I'm well?</i>

00:39.677 --> 00:41.413
Yes. We shall go
everywhere, thee and me.

00:41.449 --> 00:43.041
(SHUDDERING)

00:43.179 --> 00:44.249
I need to find Miss Ives.

00:44.274 --> 00:45.676
We all need to find Miss Ives.

00:45.739 --> 00:47.676
She is the only one who
can stop all this.

00:47.768 --> 00:49.572
ETHAN: <i>And what is "all of this?"</i>

00:49.597 --> 00:50.799
CATRIONA: <i>The End of Days.</i>

00:50.824 --> 00:52.762
Tell me where she is or I'll
put a bullet through you.

00:53.214 --> 00:55.892
She has made her choice.
Leave her in peace.

00:55.917 --> 00:58.097
I know that my destiny
is joined with hers.

00:58.122 --> 00:59.470
I will not stop.

01:01.790 --> 01:03.393
(GROWLING)

01:04.997 --> 01:05.999
(GRUNTING)

